snippet.title: Genso Suikogaiden Vol.1: Opening Sequence
snippet.description: Opening to the first Suikogaiden game, "Swordsman of Harmonia", which takes place just prior and during the events of Suikoden II.  Lots of familiar faces in the crowd.
